{"word":"G4404 - πρωΐ - prōḯ - pro-ee' - Early","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρωΐ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prōḯ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro-ee'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Early</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"உதயமாகிறபோது, அதிகாலையில், விடிந்தவுடன், காலையில் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"in the morning, early"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a>; at <i>dawn</i>; by implication the <i>day break</i> watch: - early (in the morning), (in the) morning.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}